sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant QP as Knative Queue-Proxy<br/>Istio mTLS
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant TGIS as TGIS Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/PVC)
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8086/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS (SIMPLE)
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward HTTP/8080<br/>Istio mTLS, PeerAuthentication
    QP->>Caikit: HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (pod-local)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS->>TGIS: Model inference on<br/>local model artifacts
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
    Caikit-->>QP: JSON response
    QP-->>IstioGW: Response (mTLS)
    IstioGW-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>IstioGW: gRPC call<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443, TLS (SIMPLE)
    IstioGW->>QP: gRPC/h2c/8085<br/>Istio mTLS
    QP->>Caikit: gRPC/h2c/8085<br/>plaintext (pod-local)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
    Caikit-->>QP: gRPC response
    QP-->>IstioGW: Response (mTLS)
    IstioGW-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 3: Streaming Text Generation

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443
    IstioGW->>QP: HTTP/8080 (mTLS)
    QP->>Caikit: HTTP/8080 (SSE stream)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC stream/8033
    loop Token streaming
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Generated token
        Caikit-->>QP: SSE event
        QP-->>IstioGW: Stream chunk
        IstioGW-->>Client: SSE event
    end

    Note over Prom,Caikit: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping

    Prom->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>PERMISSIVE mTLS
    Caikit-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics

    Note over Storage,TGIS: Flow 5: Model Loading (at startup)

    Storage-->>TGIS: Model artifacts downloaded<br/>by KServe storage initializer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
